<P>
   Pet peeve: Some out-of-the-ordinary flowers are hard to find.
Shipping fee chart had error.
</P>
<P>
   Shipping: Standard shipping within seven days; $4 charge for
purchases up to $15, $5 between $15.01 and $20, and so on.
</P>
