<HEADER>
A8678 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u v BC-HEARST-FEATURE-BUDGET     04-06 0650
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-HEARST-FEATURE-BUDGET-HNS </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; Thursday, April 6, 2000 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
