<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    THE STORIES BEHIND THE STORIES ABOUT GORE
 &HT;    With GORE-HYPE. Moving in (w) Washington and (f) financial
categories for release Sunday, April 9.
 &HT;    c.2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON _ In several cases, stories about Vice President Al
Gore's tendency to exaggerate his accomplishments or personal
history have been distorted themselves:
