   American Horticultural Society, 7931 East Boulevard Drive,
Alexandria, VA 22308; phone 800-942-6666; Web site
www.heattertravel.co. Offers many garden tours to unusual
destinations, including Argentina and Denmark, in conjunction with
the Leonard Haertter Travel Co.
