French cuisine, like chateaubriand bearnaise, dominates. Dinner for
two with wine, around $65.
 &HT;    For family fare, the best bargain is Bonjardim, 11 Travessa
Santo Antao, downtown off the Avenida da Liberdade. The decor is
simple and rustic, and tasty roast chicken, salad, french fries and
an earthenware jug of wine for two runs about $10.
