</P>
<P>
   and Greta Scacchi.
</P>
<P>
   A heavy-handed social melodrama whose title character is a
symbol with a capital S. Set in 1950s India, just as the country is
emerging from British rule, the movie focuses on an Anglo Indian
named Cotton Mary (Madhur Jaffrey) who insinuates herself into a
