<SLUG> BC-MEAT07-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    END URGED TO BAN ON INTERSTATE SHIPMENT OF STATE-INSPECTED MEAT
 &HT;    Moving in (w) Washington and (f) financial categories.
