<SLUG> BC-ELIAN-SCENE-0407-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    QUIET WASHINGTON SUBURB FINDS ITSELF AT CENTER OF ELIAN SAGA
 &HT;    With CUBA-ELIAN-0407.
 &HT;    Moving in both (i) International and (w) Washington categories.
 &HT;    By SUE SCHULTZ 
 &HT;    c.2000 Cox News Service 
