<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-04-06 18:20 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9113 &Cx1f; taf-z
u s BC-WOODS-COLUMN-NYT &LR;      04-06 0782
