   RETAIL-SALES (Undated) _ While a late Easter muddies the water a
bit, March's retail results offer no hard evidence that consumers
are easing up on their shopping. Talbots &AMP; Neiman Marcus posted
great results. By Chris Reidy. 500 words.
</P>
<P>
   NOVARTIS-GENERIC (Undated) _ Seven states are being asked to
prevent the sale of generic versions of cyclosporine, a drug for
people receiving human organ transplants and a $1.35 billion drug
for its developer Novartis Pharmaceuticals. By Ronald Rosenberg.
700 words.
</P>
