<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-04-06 20:16 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9296 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u s BC-TEN-COLLINS-BOS &LR;      04-06 1097
